"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?36/24/37254/abstract/32\">",
"      Kovacs JA, Kovacs AA, Polis M, et al. Cryptococcosis in the acquired immunodeficiency syndrome. Ann Intern Med 1985; 103:533.",
