"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?36/24/37254/abstract/35\">",
"      Nosanchuk JD, Shoham S, Fries BC, et al. Evidence of zoonotic transmission of Cryptococcus neoformans from a pet cockatoo to an immunocompromised patient. Ann Intern Med 2000; 132:205.",
